mesa3d-24.3.2-release-msvc.7z

Why MSVC?
MinGW is for Linux.
MSVC is a Windows native tool chain and runtime for building C/C++ executables.
MSVC will provide you with VS tools such as MFC, ATL, DirectX and GDI+.

Extract and run systemwidedeploy.cmd in a command prompt.

Select the first option
1. Core desktop OpenGL drivers

USe "GPU Caps Viewer" to test!
